data.description: Warm & welcoming 3/3.5 farmhouse. Featuring a thoughtful design and timeless selections; this home has everything you need to make you feel instantly at home! Showcasing engineered hardwood flooring, 2nd floor laundry, a gourmet kitchen with walkout, shiplapped mud room, lux primary with spacious walk-in closet, adjoined bath with Jack & Jill vanity. Versatile loft area is ideal for work from home quarters or easily converted to 4th bedroom. The finished lower level with full bath offers a functional space to suit your needs; from a guest suite to a recreational area, this space is equipped to accommodate. Outdoor living continues to impress with the stamped concrete patio,  park-like backyard and HOA community lifestyle amenities.
